6nc5hWPIsy_fSmv2bBzu9oycedOAIOGbJUuiTkicoP8NWDLxYPHU7fZntcy2OW49Sa2yDFA\"],\"rating\":4.2,\"priceLevel\":2,\"businessStatus\":\"OPERATIONAL\",\"openingHours\":[{\"start\":{\"hour\":10,\"minute\":0},\"end\":{\"hour\":21,\"minute\":0}},{\"start\":{\"hour\":11,\"minute\":0},\"end\":{\"hour\":21,\"minute\":0}},{\"start\":{\"hour\":11,\"minute\":0},\"end\":{\"hour\":21,\"minute\":0}},{\"start\":{\"hour\":11,\"minute\":0},\"end\":{\"hour\":21,\"minute\":0}},{\"start\":{\"hour\":11,\"minute\":0},\"end\":{\"hour\":21,\"minute\":0}},{\"start\":{\"hour\":10,\"minute\":0},\"end\":{\"hour\":21,\"minute\":0}}],\"formattedAddress\":\"No. 25號, Sanmin Rd, East District, Hsinchu City, Taiwan 300\",\"internationalPhoneNumber\":\"+886 3 535 6070\",\"website\":\"http://www.facebook.com/tablejoefans\",\"reviews\":[{\"author_name\":\"Bob Cook\",\"author_url\":\"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/113314347498798056711/reviews\",\"language\":\"en\",\"profile_photo_url\":\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXnVtt9YJqcF1nKU0HYeFRnAskfJtzUZjJ7wzw1xsyOyTpVQFIGmQ=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba6\",\"rating\":4,\"relative_time_description\":\"a year ago\",\"text\":\"This place has been around for a long time, and to be very honest it was looking a bit tired and worn on my previous visit. But it’s been renovated, modernized and the menu has been refreshed so it’s worth a fresh visit.\\nThe decoration is nice and minimalistic (maybe too minimalistic, for my taste  they could add a few more plants).  There were three of us dining and we opted for the steak with shrimps, a classic burger (bacon and cheese) and a burger with mushrooms and cheese. They were all really tasty. The burgers were flavorful and juicy. They also came with delicious skinny fries which were delicious and such a nice change from the greasy power coated ones that have become common recently. The steak had been cooked with garlic and was really delicious. It also came with plenty of veg, but no fries. Since some of us had the set menu we also shared a chicken quesadilla which was nice enough.\\nThe only negatives were the confusing online ordering system which was over complex for what it needed to do. The other small negative was the plants in the drinking water which had black bits on them so didn’t look nice.\\nNote that there is basically no car parking and very limited scooter parking so park at Big City as it’s very close.\\nOtherwise it was a really good experience and very tasty - recommend\",\"time\":1701151503,\"translated\":false},{\"author_name\":\"dv c313573\",\"author_url\":\"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/102818154519527910540/reviews\",\"language\":\"en\",\"profile_photo_url\":\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIJ1VFo3fK96RiGuzl-cIsdlIO5dVclwcStQF0zUlIXmjbM=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba3\",\"rating\":3,\"relative_time_description\":\"6 years ago\",\"text\":\"I’ve been in the restaurant just once. Recently I’ve been ordering online to my office. The quality of the food is average. Not the most delicious American brunch you can get. They provide you tea with it. The steak is not fresh, you get a very bad quality meat. And the salad is simple. Price is around 300 ntd per meal and it is small, not for big eaters.\",\"time\":1535282055,\"translated\":false},{\"author_name\":\"Sounak Ray\",\"author_url\":\"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/101954675229206397810/reviews\",\"language\":\"en\",\"profile_photo_url\":\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWSRQCEHDoPLvCa5q9nKQ6ZeEYaU27ohiv1t3zw5v_S9tvCbWo=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba5\",\"rating\":3,\"relative_time_description\":\"3 years ago\",\"text\":\"Been going to this place for nearly 7 years. It’s just behind big city so parking is a hassle as it gets really busy. Honestly I love the food and service here. I have tried everything from the burgers to their brunches and it’s pretty decent and it’s very fairly priced compared to other places in Hsinchu. But I haven’t seen any chance in the menu here for a long time. Their classic brunches and açaí bowl are pretty good so do try them. Their milkshakes are good but sadly they used to be better and many more options. Shared platter was alright but the cheese cake was a disappointment. If your in the neighborhood and just want a place with comfort food then have a look\",\"time\":1645510457,\"translated\":false},{\"author_name\":\"Kelly Santoso Anggani\",\"author_url\":\"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/113320009545962273669/reviews\",\"language\":\"en\",\"profile_photo_url\":\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLECKgEjvAW-NcVQiLg-PNL04fCcxJchftkz8u560VGbHJF7jqw=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba5\",\"rating\":5,\"relative_time_description\":\"6 years ago\",\"text\":\"The food is really good and service of staff is really friendly. I love the salmon pasta with truffle the taste is just right. You can order the pasta set which gives you soup, drink and desert. We choose the more expensive desert and add ntd50 and it was worth it! I recommend sharing your meal than ordering one for yourself so you can try other menus as well. I think coming here on weekdays will be less crowded and no reservations required on weekdays\",\"time\":1559653898,\"translated\":false},{\"author_name\":\"MC Lin\",\"author_url\":\"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/117882701453352114889/reviews\",\"language\":\"en\",\"profile_photo_url\":\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJzKPNhYtNieH6mZlGV0GUqvhE9GnGWOpGWszT2fYeVCWFxKg=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba4\",\"rating\":5,\"relative_time_description\":\"4 months ago\",\"text\":\"Excellent service and a few drink options offered free refills\",\"time\":1736853150,\"translated\":false}],\"currentOpeningHours\":{\"openNow\":true,\"periods\":[{\"start\":{\"hour\":10,\"minute\":0},\"end\":{\"hour\":21,\"minute\":0}},{\"start\":{\"hour\":11,\"minute\":0},\"end\":{\"hour\":21,\"minute\":0}},{\"start\":{\"hour\":11,\"minute\":0},\"end\":{\"hour\":21,\"minute\":0}},{\"start\":{\"hour\":11,\"minute\":0